### Chat/Messaging Endpoints (Not Implemented - WebSocket)

### Get User Chats
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/users/user-123/chats
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}

###

### Get Chat Details
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/chats/chat-123
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}

###

### Create or Get Chat
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/chats
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}

{
  "sender_id": "user-123",
  "receiver_id": "user-456",
  "order_id": "order-123"
}

###

### Update Last Message
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/v1/chats/chat-123/last-message
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}

{
  "message": "Order has been delivered!"
}

###

### Get Chat Messages
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/chats/chat-123/messages?limit=50&offset=0
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}

###

### Send Message
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/chats/chat-123/messages
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}

{
  "id": "msg-123",
  "chat_id": "chat-123",
  "content": "Hello! How is my order coming along?",
  "sender_id": "user-123",
  "receiver_id": "user-456",
  "message_type": "text"
}

###

### Mark Message as Read
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/v1/messages/msg-123/read
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}

###

### Delete Message
DELETE http://localhost:8080/api/v1/messages/msg-123
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}

###

### Get Chats Stream (Not Implemented - WebSocket)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/users/user-123/chats/stream
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}

###

### Get Messages Stream (Not Implemented - WebSocket)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/chats/chat-123/messages/stream
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}

###

### Get New Messages Stream (Not Implemented - WebSocket)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/chats/chat-123/new-messages/stream
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}

